				<ext:value>description-en:
The movie related to this poster is &quot;Alif Laila&quot;, which was directed by K.Amarnath and released in 1953. Two of the main actors, probably Vijay Kumar and Asha Mathur, can be seen close to a wall of a palace like building. He is sitting on the wall where as she is standing at a distance. In the background, towers are depicted. The  stairs in the front have patterns typical of Mughal period architecture. (gs/sp)</ext:value>
